  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TombOfServilii.TopicData
  topicTitle: Historical Importance
  contentText: Standing along the Via Appia, the tomb has witnessed centuries of
    Roman history. Today, its ruins offer modern archaeologists vital insights into
    Roman engineering, burial laws, artistic customs, and the social stratification
    of Roman nobility.
  narrationClip: {fileID: 0}
  subtitleText: Standing along the Via Appia, the tomb offers insights into Roman
    engineering and customs.
